net.wequick.small.webkit

Class JsResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.wequick.small.webkit.JsResult

  • public class JsResult
extends java.lang.Object
    An instance of this class is passed as a parameter in various WebViewClient action notifications. The object is used as a handle onto the underlying JavaScript-originated request, and provides a means for the client to indicate whether this action should proceed.

      Callback interface, implemented by the WebViewClient implementation to receive notifications when the JavaScript result represented by a JsResult instance has finished.
